title: Wall Street Breakfast May 2: U.S. Housing Affordability Nears Record Low
author: Seeking Alpha

description: U.S. Housing Affordability nears record low as mortgage rates keep climbing. Moderna expects COVID vaccine for kids under 6 to be ready for June review and the Novavax vaccine also considered in June. Twitter deal spread indicates uncertainty about Musk closing acquisition.
